headline: Realtor.com速 Data Shows the "Pool Premium" Is More Than a Pandemic Trend
summary: As Memorial Day kicks off the summer season, a new analysis of Realtor.com速 listing data finds that while the pandemic-driven surge in swimming pool premiums has subsided, pools still command a significant price advantage, and the share of listings featuring pools reached an all-time high this April.
